{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udfae\u2728 <strong>Step into the enchanting world of T.I.MO!</strong> \u2728\ud83c\udfae</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf0e <strong>See the world through the eyes of a child!</strong> <strong>Triaventuras</strong> is a whimsical 2D point-and-click puzzle adventure where YOU take control of three unique characters\u2014Mao, Pao, and Clau. Each one magically sees the world, and it\u2019s up to you to use their perspectives to solve puzzles, outsmart riddles, and help adorable monsters find their way home. \ud83c\udfe1\ud83d\udc3e</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701340/extras/STEAM_38401240_003.png?t=1733497646\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> \ud83d\udd0d <strong>Core mechanic:</strong> The solution is always right before you, but the right point of view makes all the difference! Shift between perspectives to unlock secrets, explore colorful worlds and unleash your inner problem solver. \ud83e\udde9\ud83d\udca1</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701340/extras/Clau.gif?t=1733497646\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83e\uddd9\u200d\u2642\ufe0f Along the way, meet the legendary <strong>Mohan</strong>\u2014a mythological spirit who\u2019s lost his magic and his way. Mao, Pao, and Clau must recover his magical items to restore his powers and return him to the river he calls home. \ud83c\udf0a\u2728</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1701340/extras/Mao.gif?t=1733497646\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udca1 <strong>What are you waiting for?</strong> Dive into this heartfelt, brain-bending adventure and discover the world like never before.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p